id="how-to-start-a-restaurant-section9-step3" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.3&nbsp;</span><h4 id=create-marketing-campaigns>Create marketing campaigns.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-use-marketing-campaigns-288x288-20200825.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Create marketing campaigns."></div></div><p>Set up text, email, and radio marketing campaigns. You can also approach print media such as magazines and newspapers to run advertisements.</p></div></div><div
id="how-to-start-a-restaurant-section9-step4" class="step"><div
class="step-desc"><div
class="step-title">
<span>9.4&nbsp;</span><h4 id=use-local-seo>Use local SEO.</h4></div><div
class="image-wrapper"><div
class="image-holder">
<img
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-use-local-seo-288x288-20200825.jpeg?crop=1:1,smart&width=144&dpr=2" class="lazyload" width="144" height="144" alt="Use local SEO."></div></div><p>Ideally, when someone does a search for a local restaurant, like "best restaurants near me," you should be prominent in the results. You can learn how to make that happen for your business using local search engine optimization (SEO) techniques, Google My Business, and Yelp!</p><div
class="step-tip">
<span
class="icon">
