class="container"><h2 id=fAQs class="section-heading">FAQs:</h2><div
class="row"><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-can-i-start-a-food-business-in-new-york class="question">How can I start a food business in New York?</h3><div
class="answer"><ol><li>Decide on what type of food business it is you want to start.</li><li>Form a business entity.</li><li>Apply for an EIN.</li><li>Secure funding.</li><li>Open a business bank account.</li><li>Register for tax.</li><li>Find a location.</li><li>Get licenses from the Division of Food Safety and Inspection.</li><li>Hire employees.</li><li>Source ingredients.</li><li>Buy equipment.</li><li>Get insurance.</li><li>Market your business.</li></ol></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=what-is-the-startup-cost-for-a-restaurant class="question">What is the startup cost for a restaurant?</h3><div
class="answer"><p><a
href="#cost-of-starting-a-restaurant">Startup costs for a restaurant</a> depend on the type of restaurant you are looking to open. A diner can cost about $200,000 to set up, while a fast-food franchise can cost between $10,000 and $2.5 million.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-start-a-small-restaurant class="question">How do I start a small restaurant?</h3><div
class="answer"><ol><li><a
href="#conduct-market-research">Research your concept, customer base, and competitors</a>.</li><li><a
href="#develop-a-menu-suited-to-your-target-market">Develop and test a menu suited to your customer base</a>.</li><li><a
href="#choose-a-name-and-trademark-it">Choose a name and trademark it</a>.</li><li><a
href="#write-a-business-plan">Create a business plan</a>.</li><li><a
href="#form-your-restaurant-business">Form your restaurant business</a>.</li><li><a
href="#decide-on-a-location">Decide on a location</a>.</li><li><a
href="#secure-financing">Use your business plan to secure financing</a>.</li><li><a
href="#secure-and-prepare-your-space">Set up your space</a>.</li><li><a
href="#build-your-team">Build your team</a>.</li><li><a
href="#market-your-restaurant">Market your restaurant</a>.</li><li><a
href="#complete-the-final-checks-before-your-grand-opening">Hold a grand opening</a>.</li></ol></div></div><div
